  "text": "where V is the volume of the solution (ml), and α and k o are constants. The plot obtained according to Eq. (12) is not satisfactorily linear. This shows that the bulk diffusion of MB into the pores of SW was not the only rate limiting step [CITATION_1] and it may be due to the both film and pore diffusion. The kinetic parameters are presented in Table 7 . ). ). ). ",
